HEADWORD: Queller
<hw>Quell"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A killer;
<as>as, Jack the Giant <ex>Queller</ex></as>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Wyclif (Mark vi. 27).</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who quells; one who overpowers or
subdues.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quellio</ent>⟦br⟧
